f2b5bb9c689f68ba912b1","tid":83691,"uid":71851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170117/large/1484616942_f8d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F1484616942_f8d3.jpg&h=02ffb500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌晨4時許，28歲模特兒伍淑怡(YoYo)，在facebook網絡直播跳海自殺實況。她在觀塘啟興道九龍貨倉旁的海濱長廊，在鏡頭前吐心事近一小時，哭訴「生活好辛苦」、「對唔住媽咪細佬」，然後放下手機，爬出圍欄外。facebook上的朋友不斷勸止，有人報警，與YoYo在同一模特兒公司工作的練樂怡，馬上從大埔住所乘的士趕到現場。當時YoYo剛被消防員救起，稍後送院治理。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170117/large/1484609820_3c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F1484609820_3c16.jpg&h=12ee3ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方調查後稱，YoYo疑為感情問題困擾。練樂怡趕到醫院探望，感嘆地表示，拜仁連撬兩賀芬咸主力當時網上有很多人看到直播，但未有人即時以行動趕去現場救人。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170117/large/1484609821_b1b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F1484609821_b1b9.jpg&h=5956d8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYoyo在facebook網上直播的片段長達2個多小時，直至警員到達現場撿起手機，直播始告中斷。她在facebook說，我知道我這一刻，做的事會令大家很失望，很感謝一直以來支持我的朋友，我母親一直疼愛我，放心很快沒有事，只是想將我想說的話說出，很感謝所有支持我的粉絲，很感謝大家，我真的很辛苦，真的很討厭我自己。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170117/large/1484616198_3514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F1484616198_3514.jpg&h=8ec4980c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今早8時30分許，在病房中的YoYo再在facebook進行直播，對於自己的行為感到抱歉，「對唔住，令到大家咁擔心」，指出自己事發前有飲酒，但沒有「揩嘢(吸毒)」。YoYo隨後又留言:「對不起我完全忘記了自己發生過什麼事，摩根大通預計2017年中國經濟增長6.5%要大家擔心真的十分對不起，醫生說我現在有低溫症所以不能出院，十分感謝在我出事時來探訪我的朋友，對不起，<span style=\"color: red;\">細佬媽咪老豆爸爸媽媽</span>所有關心我的好友真的對不起，我真的完全忘記了發生什麼事。」</blockquote><br />\n咩媽咪老豆爸爸媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e265a2889a8c4db7a23cb67ad9ed83ee51b60623","tid":83691,"uid":5386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:48:25.000Z","msg":"拜仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇左幾次都唔知做乜鳩"},{"pid":"f0cc29c713cbfe389c710596c38db0bba8a93e1a","tid":83691,"uid":14510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:48:33.000Z","msg":"有冇片or fb link?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f742363df2dd3f11dab3cf1f4b0667586d737ebd","tid":83691,"uid":43972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:49:35.000Z","msg":"拜仁連撬兩賀芬咸主力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a09c7d19a0f331c8b566ac3e48572888f19508","tid":83691,"uid":25036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170117/large/1484616942_f8d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F1484616942_f8d3.jpg&h=02ffb500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌晨4時許，28歲模特兒伍淑怡(YoYo)，在facebook網絡直播跳海自殺實況。她在觀塘啟興道九龍貨倉旁的海濱長廊，在鏡頭前吐心事近一小時，哭訴「生活好辛苦」、「對唔住媽咪細佬」，然後放下手機，爬出圍欄外。facebook上的朋友不斷勸止，有人報警，與YoYo在同一模特兒公司工作的練樂怡，馬上從大埔住所乘的士趕到現場。當時YoYo剛被消防員救起，稍後送院治理。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170117/large/1484609820_3c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F1484609820_3c16.jpg&h=12ee3ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方調查後稱，YoYo疑為